{"tid":18654,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"屌 的士佬真係好仆街","createTime":"2016-12-02T11:49:58.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-02T14:00:20.000Z","uid":20337,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fe717908ab153b30dc104943c0c3b2a7d46cbd87","tid":18654,"uid":20337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T11:49:58.000Z","msg":"是咁的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我愉翠出新蒲崗四美街<br />\n好正常地一定係行大老山隧道<br />\n一出轉幾轉就到<br />\n你老母佢同我行獅子山隧道<br />\n我同frd傾計唔為意<br />\n一發現窗外景色有異 即刻就問<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> :做乜唔行大老山啊?<br />\n條撚樣話哎呀我冇諗到行大老山啊<br />\n我心諗 屌你喇行遠路仲扮傻<br />\n本身$4x嘅車費變成$86<br />\n仲搞到我地遲咗勁多<br />\n落車嗰陣比一舊水佢找得十蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> :唉 四十幾蚊比你行到八十幾<br />\n佢仲好大聲話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁你出聲啊嘛<br />\n出你老母咩 正常人根本唔會捨近取遠<br />\n你食飯都唔閪會提人張開口喇<br />\n最後個司機姓呂 車牌NT2717<br />\n各巴絲自己留神<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88a8c97550c52b23a521f5157b9ce25c6d978f20","tid":18654,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T11:51:01.000Z","msg":"報警啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 最憎的士佬係度扮傻"},{"pid":"d922bd0e8dbcacdd49d3ce9dd7737d8c3ef85717","tid":18654,"uid":21028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T11:51:27.000Z","msg":"報警啦"},{"pid":"e20a90fac752b999c2eaedd78966a7ad7972af24","tid":18654,"uid":20337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T11:53:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>報警啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 最憎的士佬係度扮傻</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n嗰幾十蚊好小事<br />\n啖氣難下咽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBetween 有得報警咖?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50b8fe8d68ad96979939d011e90157577291379e","tid":18654,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T11:54:13.000Z","msg":"到左之後唔落車報警 應該得未試過"},{"pid":"e03c35907dc8de8d0910cbf9bdfae1e3cff4b151","tid":18654,"uid":20337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T11:56:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>到左之後唔落車報警 應該得未試過</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n趕時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係我冇撚用 我走住嚟屌😭"},{"pid":"2baa5c36924ee4ec942d6fd233a91babf86e6986","tid":18654,"uid":9115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T11:57:48.000Z","msg":"廢老<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 廢中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 廢青<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n形容多少少唔該<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9315a0cd9b22025c7540c389500b6844c7b6187","tid":18654,"uid":34677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T12:01:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>報警啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 最憎的士佬係度扮傻</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n嗰幾十蚊好小事<br />\n啖氣難下咽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBetween 有得報警咖?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n梗係得 俾我玩大佢"},{"pid":"0465065c1d5e533b17d73ba99e42d774779ed91e","tid":18654,"uid":20820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T12:04:07.000Z","msg":"警犬有拉過濫收車資，兜遠路唔肯定入唔入到"},{"pid":"cec856a9b9379d68febaab110e94313425b35146","tid":18654,"uid":20337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T12:07:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>廢老<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 廢中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 廢青<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n形容多少少唔該<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n廢中嚟<br />\n唔找錢嗰吓神級仆街"},{"pid":"4f3758f0ca3a10690d14c7eb1c0ac0f0df381022","tid":18654,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T12:08:34.000Z","msg":"你男定女呀 同佢鬥大聲丫嘛"},{"pid":"d154a3732f2b12e623be1e9dca803cf7dc6fbaf5","tid":18654,"uid":4525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T12:10:36.000Z","msg":"報警拉佢"},{"pid":"e68e73e71f58bc7b3fa25a3dd560cf4d48c26f70","tid":18654,"uid":41967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T12:16:03.000Z","msg":"講真，四十幾蚊出到新浦崗得唔得呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我就唔係咁信喇。<br />\n所以我次次上親的士都叫定佢點行，唔識行我教埋你行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48afb6a485eb332de1a079ffaff808c0c8ebff27","tid":18654,"uid":28309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T12:18:48.000Z","msg":"今日先見到個仆街的士佬拒載<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a9de2a1ff7701be2c34e299121f9deb3816e9e0","tid":18654,"uid":28795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T12:26:21.000Z","msg":"屋企兩老去QE覆診，由土瓜灣樂民村出發搭撚左60蚊！好蝦唔蝦，蝦老人家，嗰個正仆街的士狗！<br />\n<br />\n一日都係我唔好冇跟去，如果唔係屌到隻狗化撚開"},{"pid":"b2f275237ec7933efadc8e035a27f6f44861389b","tid":18654,"uid":20625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T12:34:15.000Z","msg":"上次係同學做功課做到太夜（凌晨2點走）<br />\n唔記得左搭0630既機同老母去日本玩<br />\n咁好啦，天水圍飛番淺水灣<br />\n我預都係400-500<br />\n咁我去問價啦<br />\n<br />\n啊，屌你老母<br />\n第一個開我價800<br />\n頭也不回轉身就走<br />\n<br />\n第二個仲撚好笑<br />\n同我講話載完你要空車番新界<br />\n開我價800/900<br />\n我話：咁你搵第二個客啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbff90c0ad7429f1177565a46367573eb763ce72","tid":18654,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"s